# Task 2: Nmap Scripting Engine (NSE) Integration

## Overview
This folder documents the use of the Nmap Scripting Engine (NSE) to extend
basic port scanning into active service enumeration and vulnerability
detection. NSE uses Lua scripts organised into categories. All scripts were
run on Kali Linux against localhost and the Metasploitable 2 target
(192.168.56.101).

